{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
GIFT TIERS BAR
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Custom addition to the Impact theme, not part of Maestrooo's base code. Renders the progress bar toward the free gift
tiers and hands the configuration to assets/custom-gift-tiers.js, which adds and removes the gift line.

Replaces the "Monster Cart Upsell+Free Gifts" app. Kept in its own snippet so free-shipping-bar.liquid stays untouched
and a future Impact update has nothing to conflict with.

********************************************
How the promise is actually kept
********************************************

This snippet and its script only decide how many gift units sit in the cart. The price comes from the Shopify automatic
discount "Cadeau palier - 1 Booster offert par tranche de 80 EUR (max 2)", which was verified on the live store:

* it repeats once per completed 80 EUR step, capped at 2 per order
* any gift unit beyond the entitlement is charged at full price, so over-adding cannot be exploited

A single gift product with a varying quantity is used rather than one product per tier, because two automatic discounts
do not stack outside Shopify Plus. That was measured on this store: the second discount simply overrode the first.

********************************************
SAFETY GATE
********************************************

gift_tiers_enabled must stay false whenever the automatic discount is paused, deleted or edited to no longer cover this
variant. The gift carries a real 5 EUR price, and the discount is the only thing bringing it to 0. Enabled without a
matching discount, this would add a priced line labelled as a gift and the customer would be charged for it.

********************************************
Configuration
********************************************

* gift_variant_id must be ACTIVE and published to the Online Store, otherwise /cart/update.js answers 404 "Cannot find
  variant" and no gift is ever added. That is exactly how the previous app broke.
* Thresholds are in cents of the shop currency (EUR). Other markets are converted at runtime.
* The number of thresholds must not exceed the discount's per-order cap, or the bar would promise more than checkout
  grants.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign gift_tiers_enabled = true

  assign gift_variant_id = 50520683020616
  assign gift_reward = 'Booster offert'
  assign gift_thresholds = '8000,16000' | split: ','
-%}

{%- if gift_tiers_enabled -%}
  {%- liquid
    # The gift must not count toward the goal that unlocks it

    assign eligible_subtotal = 0

    for line_item in cart.items
      unless line_item.variant_id == gift_variant_id
        assign eligible_subtotal = eligible_subtotal | plus: line_item.final_line_price
      endunless
    endfor

    assign cart_discount = 0

    for discount_application in cart.cart_level_discount_applications
      assign cart_discount = cart_discount | plus: discount_application.total_allocated_amount
    endfor

    assign eligible_subtotal = eligible_subtotal | minus: cart_discount

    if eligible_subtotal < 0
      assign eligible_subtotal = 0
    endif

    capture config_json
      echo '{"variantId":'
      echo gift_variant_id
      echo ',"reward":'
      echo gift_reward | json
      echo ',"thresholds":['
      echo gift_thresholds | join: ','
      echo ']}'
    endcapture
  -%}

  <gift-tiers-bar
    class="free-shipping-bar gift-tiers-bar"
    config="{{ config_json | escape }}"
    subtotal="{{ eligible_subtotal }}"
    unreached-message="{{ 'cart.gift_tiers.limit_unreached_html' | t: remaining_amount: '@@remaining@@', reward: '@@reward@@' | escape }}"
    all-reached-message="{{ 'cart.gift_tiers.all_reached_html' | t | escape }}"
  >
    {%- comment -%}Placeholder filled in by JS, mirroring how free-shipping-bar does it{%- endcomment -%}
    <span data-gift-tiers-message>&nbsp;</span>

    <progress-bar class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" style="--progress: 0"></progress-bar>
  </gift-tiers-bar>
{%- endif -%}
